latestIgtvVideos.caption:
AD/ If you’re a fan of aloe vera gel - I’m pretty sure it doesn’t get any better than this. 
@sadhev aloe and saffron gel is a lightweight concoction that can be used as a moisturiser or overnight as a leave-on mask (like I do whenever I come back home after spending time in the Sun). It instantly calms and hydrates my skin.
It’s packed with saffron and kumkumadi tailam which is known for reducing pigmentation.
It’s sweet scent, little strands of pure saffron and soothing texture all packed into one jar, give you a multisensorial experience, definitely worth checking out.

#SkincareWithSadhev
